Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也加入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？你也是同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  大家都要玩這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修哉也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修哉不喜歡和姐姐不一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事沒…又好像有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過就沒有敵人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了啊  塗鴉戰隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  我是怪人眼鏡大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字好土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  你也變身和我們一起戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要讓這傢伙也戴上眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你得逞的！站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點跟上來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  蕾說的是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電話裡說爸爸媽媽被捲進塌方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有找到媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受夠了  為什麼總是我們遭這樣的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以為好不容易能夠變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  大家都不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的房間還沒關門？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次偷偷溜進去還被罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還沒鎖上  應該行的吧
